SUMMARY:Tesla Gigafactory Berlin Tour 2026
DESCRIPTION:Tesla has invited the official owners club of the United Kingdo
 m to a private tour of their Gigafactory Berlin-Brandenburg for 2026. We m
 eet in Berlin on Sunday 18 October for our club reception and dinner\, and
  the have the factory tour in the morning of Monday 19 October. This makes
  it flexible for a long weekend visit or tagging onto a longer road trip. 
 Please note that registration has now closed for 2026 and we will be conta
 cting members shortly if they have been successful in receiving a ticket i
 n the member ballot. Over 18s only. No press or media\; this is a special 
 visit for TOUK members.\n\nListing: October 18th–19th\, 2026\n\nWall clock
  / source TZ: Europe/London\n\nEvent & tickets (Ti.to): https://ti.to/tesl
 aownersuk/tesla-gigafactory-berlin-tour-2026-copy\n\nSource list: upcoming
